  "prob_desc_output_spec": "Print the maximum possible number x such that Ivan can distribute the cake in such a way that each plate will contain at least x pieces of cake.",
  "source_code": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nint min (int a, int b)\n{\n\tif (a<b)\n\t\treturn a;\n\telse\n\t\treturn b;\n}\n\nint main (void)\n{\n\tint n, a, b, max=0;\n\tscanf (\"%d %d %d\", &n, &a, &b);\n\n\tint i;\n\tfor (i=1 ; i<n ; i++)\n\t{\n\t\tif (max < min((a/i), (b/(n-i))))\n\t\t\tmax=min((a/i), (b/(n-i)));\n\t}\n\n\tprintf(\"%d\", max);\n\n\treturn 0;\n}",
